{"tid":1048800,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"希斯路機場等倫敦三處收郵包炸彈　拆開爆炸引發小火","createTime":"2019-03-06T00:29:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-06T00:46:26.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f1002a277a200ba2f02c96068a241174e29d6901","tid":1048800,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T00:29:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190306/large/1551810880_8889.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190306%2Flarge%2F1551810880_8889.jpg&h=9d212927&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其中一個包裹拆開時爆炸。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190306/large/1551810091_1285.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190306%2Flarge%2F1551810091_1285.jpg&h=29f16650&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n倫敦交通樞紐收小型郵包炸彈，包裹貼了愛爾蘭郵票。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190306/large/1551805002_9dd0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190306%2Flarge%2F1551805002_9dd0.jpg&h=15dd48c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警方在滑鐵盧站調查。<br />\n<br />\n英國倫敦希斯路機場、城市機場和滑鐵盧車站周二收到小型土製炸彈包裹，警方視三宗郵包炸彈發現案相關，已展開反恐調查，暫時無人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n英國天空新聞報道，寄到希斯路機場的包裹，拆開時發生爆炸引致小火，辦公大樓一度要疏散，無人受傷。<br />\n<br />\n警方指包裹貼了愛爾蘭郵票，由都柏林寄出。愛爾蘭警方介入調查。<br />\n<br />\n該三個地方的辦公大樓幾小時內先後發現可疑包裹，警方接報後到三處調查，發現A4紙大小的郵袋內藏另一郵袋內，內有土製炸彈，初步調查顯示，若開啟「似乎可引致小火」，現已被安全處理。事件中無人受傷。<br />\n<br />\n該三大交通樞紐運作未受事件影響。<br />\n<br />\n路透社／英國廣播公司／英國《每日郵報》／《每日鏡報》<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190306/59335142\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190306%2F59335142&d=tUmqA7E7lgkQFc9zeVIKXmrU9%2B1YVtZAf0CByt%2F7qsI%3D&h=b967fd85\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190306%2F59335142&h=aca9d7a1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190306/59335142</a>"},{"pid":"edc8939ee8da9d567dcfc91c93304a96ed6b839e","tid":1048800,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T00:46:26.000Z","msg":"愛爾蘭共和軍"}]}